  contradictoryClaimId: CL001
  explanationText: "Simon claims he stayed all evening. His valet ticket shows his
    car left at 8:22 PM \u2014 nearly 3 hours before closing. Press photos confirm
    he vanished from sight after 8 PM. The warehouse break-in occurred at 9:15 PM,
    giving Simon time to drive there after retrieving his car. He was not at the
    gallery all night."
